                            We designed GreggsJobs with a community of job seekers and employers in mind. A community where job seekers can give and get 
                            feedback from employers to improve their job seeking skills and resumes. To often when people apply for jobs online, they get 
                            little to no feedback or response from the company they are applying with. At GreggsJobs we are focusing on encouraging employers 
                            to be more communicative with applicants so they can improve their resumes and skills to match what employers are looking for.
                        </div>
                    </div>
