                           skill level. As of now, at GreggsJobs, you can filter your job search by category, Full-time or Part-time listings. As a guest at 
                           the website you can browse job listings, company listings, and read company reviews left by other GreggsJobs members. In order to take 
                           full advantage of the website and apply for jobs, or leave reviews, you need to create a free account using your name and email address. 
